title: Community Laundry Room, Patio / Balcony, Online Maintenance Request
posting_body: ['Welcome To The 800 at Bellshire', 'Bellshire Apartments offer one and two bedroom apartment homes in Conroe, TX.', 'Our community has two swimming pools, laundry facilities, BBQ areas and more.', 'All apartments include central air and heat, electric range/ovens, frost-free refrigerators, garbage disposals, dishwashers, vent hoods, and private patio or balcony.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 81', 'OR Text', '81', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 947 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Smoke Detectors', '- 1 and 2 Bedroom Floorplans', '- Full Size Laundry Connections*', '- Ceiling Fans', '- Tile Floors', '- Kitchens Include Frost-free Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Range/Oven', '- Trash, Pest control, and Water are included in the rent.', '- Patio / Balcony', '*Some features available in select homes.', 'Available features subject to change.', 'Community Amenities', '- BBQ Grill', '- Near public Transportation', '- Online Maintenance Request', '- Convenient Parking', '- Playground', '- Picnic/ BBQ Area', '- Close to Library', '- Community Laundry Room', '- Close to Downtown District', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Friendly community** (Call for Details)', '** Restrictions may apply.', 'The 800 at Bellshire Apartments', '800 Bellshire , Conroe, TX, 77301', 'masyOyB1']
